  "texts": [
    "This combination can help provide a more comprehensive understanding of the factors that influence academic performance because a predictive model can capture a complete picture of a student's situation.",
    "Even though many DL techniques have been developed to measure the student's academic performance and find student's at risk of failure, There are still some issues that have not been solved yet.",
    "These issues include:",
    "• There is an ambiguity in the meaning of success and dropout among the studies that have been reviewed, which will have an impact on how to identify and handle.",
    "• Hybrid models need further investigation, as these models have the ability to produce competitive prediction accuracy."
  ]
